text: Leo Weinkauf (born 7 July 1996) is a German footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for MSV Duisburg, on loan from Hannover 96. ==Career== Weinkauf moved to MSV Duisburg on 18 June 2019, on loan from Hannover 96. He made his professional debut in the 3.
